<div id="projects" class="py-12 ">
    <div class="d-flex align-center mb-8">
        <MudText Typo="Typo.h5"
                 Color="Color.Primary"
                 Style="font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px;">
            Project
        </MudText>
        <MudDivider Class="ml-4 flex-grow-1 section-divider" />
    </div>

    <MudPaper Class="pa-8" Elevation="0"
        Style="background-color: var(--mud-palette-surface);
            border: 1.5px solid var(--mud-palette-divider);
            border-radius: 28px; overflow: hidden;">
        <MudGrid Spacing="4">
            <MudItem xs="12" md="6"
                Class="d-flex flex-column justify-center mb-12">
                
                <MudStack Row="true"
                          AlignItems="AlignItems.Center"
                          Class="mb-4">
                    <MudAvatar Style="background-color: var(--mud-palette-divider);"
                               Size="Size.Small">
                        <MudIcon Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.RestaurantMenu"
                                 Color="Color.Primary"
                                 Size="Size.Small" />
                    </MudAvatar>
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1"
                             Style="font-weight: 800;
                                    color: var(--mud-palette-text-primary);">
                        Bento Order System
                    </MudText>
                </MudStack>

                <MudText Typo="Typo.body2"
                         Style="color: var(--mud-palette-text-secondary);
                                line-height: 1.8;"
                        Class="mb-5">
                    <b>餐點訂購自動化方案</b>：整合 Blazor Server 與 Line Bot 實現在線點餐與自動下單。
                    <br />
                    <span style="font-size: 0.8rem;">
                        • <b>自動統計</b>：每日準時結單，精準計算餐點數量。<br />
                        • <b>Line 整合</b>：自動發送訂單給供應商，流程全自動。<br />
                        • <b>奶油風 UI</b>：極簡介面設計，提升員工訂餐意願。
                    </span>
                </MudText>

                <div class="d-flex gap-2 mb-6">
                    <MudChip T="string"
                             Size="Size.Small"
                             Variant="Variant.Filled"
                             Style="background: var(--mud-palette-divider);
                                    color: var(--mud-palette-primary);
                                    font-weight: 600;">
                            Completed
                    </MudChip>
                    <MudChip T="string"
                             Size="Size.Small"
                             Variant="Variant.Text" 
                             Style="background: var(--mud-palette-divider);
                                    color: var(--mud-palette-primary);
                                    font-weight: 600;">
                        .NET 10
                    </MudChip>
                </div>
                
                <div class="d-flex gap-3 mt-auto">
                    <MudButton Variant="Variant.Text"
                               StartIcon="@Icons.Custom.Brands.GitHub"
                               Color="Color.Primary"
                               Style="font-weight: 700;"
                               Target="_blank"
                               Href="https://github.com/th0225/bento-order">
                        CODE
                    </MudButton>
                    <MudButton Variant="Variant.Filled"
                               Disabled
                               Color="Color.Primary"
                               Style="border-radius: 12px;
                                      font-weight: 700;">
                        LIVE DEMO
                    </MudButton>
                </div>
            </MudItem>

            <MudItem xs="12" md="6" Class="mockup-container">
                <MudImage Src="images/bento-desktop.png" 
                          Alt="Desktop Preview"
                          Class="mockup-desktop" />
                
                <MudImage Src="images/bento-mobile.png" 
                          Alt="Mobile Preview"
                          Class="mockup-mobile" />
            </MudItem>
        </MudGrid>
    </MudPaper>

    <MudPaper Class="pa-8 mt-6" Elevation="0"
        Style="background-color: var(--mud-palette-surface);
            border: 1.5px solid var(--mud-palette-divider);
            border-radius: 28px; overflow: hidden;">
        <MudGrid Spacing="4">
            <MudItem xs="12" md="6"
                Class="d-flex flex-column justify-center mb-12">
                
                <MudStack Row="true"
                          AlignItems="AlignItems.Center"
                          Class="mb-4">
                    <MudAvatar Style="background-color: var(--mud-palette-divider);"
                               Size="Size.Small">
                        <MudIcon Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.Radar"
                                 Color="Color.Primary"
                                 Size="Size.Small" />
                    </MudAvatar>
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1"
                             Style="font-weight: 800;
                                    color: var(--mud-palette-text-primary);">
                        Auto Catch
                    </MudText>
                </MudStack>

                <MudText Typo="Typo.body2"
                         Style="color: var(--mud-palette-text-secondary);
                                line-height: 1.8;"
                        Class="mb-5">
                    <b>PTT 趨勢即時雷達</b>：基於 Playwright 與 Blazor 的多看板監控系統。
                    <br />
                    <span style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #8D7B68;">
                        • <b>並行監控</b>：支援 3 組看板同步抓取，自定義推文門檻與回文過濾。<br />
                        • <b>性能優化</b>：實作全域單例服務與快取機制，大幅提升頁面導航流暢度。<br />
                        • <b>精確控制</b>：整合 CancellationToken 實現非同步任務即時中止，節省資源。
                    </span>
                </MudText>

                <div class="d-flex gap-2 mb-6">
                    <MudChip T="string"
                             Size="Size.Small"
                             Variant="Variant.Outlined"
                             Style="background: var(--mud-palette-divider);
                                    color: var(--mud-palette-primary);
                                    font-weight: 600;">
                            In Progress
                    </MudChip>
                    <MudChip T="string"
                             Size="Size.Small"
                             Variant="Variant.Text" 
                             Style="background: var(--mud-palette-divider);
                                    color: var(--mud-palette-primary);
                                    font-weight: 600;">
                        .NET 10
                    </MudChip>
                </div>
                
                <div class="d-flex gap-3 mt-auto mb-6">
                    <MudButton Variant="Variant.Text"
                               StartIcon="@Icons.Custom.Brands.GitHub"
                               Color="Color.Primary"
                               Style="font-weight: 700;"
                               Target="_blank"
                               Href="https://github.com/th0225/Auto-Catch">
                        CODE
                    </MudButton>
                    <MudButton Variant="Variant.Filled"
                               Disabled
                               Color="Color.Primary"
                               Style="border-radius: 12px;
                                      font-weight: 700;">
                        LIVE DEMO
                    </MudButton>
                </div>
            </MudItem>

            <MudItem xs="12" md="6" Class="mockup-container">
                <MudImage Src="images/catch-desktop.jpeg" 
                          Alt="Desktop Preview"
                          Class="mockup-desktop" />
                
                <MudImage Src="images/catch-mobile.jpeg" 
                          Alt="Mobile Preview"
                          Class="mockup-mobile" />
            </MudItem>
        </MudGrid>
    </MudPaper>
</div>

@code {
